{"tid":1161393,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊去旅行，都未開始第一日已經激嬲我","createTime":"2019-05-19T07:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T11:20:27.000Z","uid":78971,"like":4,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"75f3dca5892065d2c06f18d4210ef785302920ee","tid":1161393,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"第一次同男朋友去旅行，<br />\n去日本玩下做下嘢咁（唔洗講到出口啦...）<br />\n<br />\n去到當地，到埋酒店，<br />\n<br />\n佢解鎖個篋，「5，2，6」<br />\n我問佢：「點解用『5，2，6』呀？」<br />\n佢：「講咗出嚟就唔係密碼啦」<br />\n我：「係咪ex嘅生日？」（因為佢生日唔係呢日）<br />\n佢又答返我：「講咗出嚟就唔係密碼啦」<br />\n<br />\n根本係佢ex嘅生日，我而家嬲咗佢<br />\n佢唔講出嚟唔洗止意我會同佢一齊瞓<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n只求有個地方呻下"},{"pid":"ac25817abd2ae1fb78dcf95973739891fcb23035","tid":1161393,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:15:40.000Z","msg":"利申：我可能識佢Ex..."},{"pid":"6f169c935c3600f1a64be14236e2c9b1db8b73b1","tid":1161393,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:18:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要懲罰佢<br />\n屌足佢526下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"94d4fd5c116fffa4cc1070b62cb72e70bce9f001","tid":1161393,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ac25817abd2ae1fb78dcf95973739891fcb23035","tid":1161393,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:15:40.000Z","msg":"利申：我可能識佢Ex..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:19:49.000Z","msg":"點解咁講"},{"pid":"b5b26ed528ce0c2aa93957dbcedbac5c27fde767","tid":1161393,"uid":223790,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"446a36a05cc53bb13b5d0c38b3dd6aeaa8b30d50","tid":1161393,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"b5b26ed528ce0c2aa93957dbcedbac5c27fde767","tid":1161393,"uid":223790,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"